      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: 7th level, hex spell or a warlock feature that curses</em><br />Your curse creates a temporary bond between you and your target. As a bonus action, you can magically teleport up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space you can see within 5 feet of the target cursed by your hex spell or by a warlock feature of yours, such as Hexblade's Curse or Sign of Ill Omen. To teleport in this way, you must be able to see the cursed target.</p><p><em>This may be invoked in place of one of your Eldritch Blast beams.</em></p>",
